    <item>
      <title>中国央行通过增加临时回购来加强对利率的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/pboc-to-conduct-temporary-repos-depending-on-market-conditions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行下午除进行上午的常规操作外，还将进行临时债券回购或逆回购操作，加强对短期利率的调控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/pboc-to-conduct-temporary-repos-depending-on-market-conditions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 00:18:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风暴和野火对产量构成双重威胁，油价保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商追踪美国风暴和加拿大野火对生产构成的双重威胁，油价在连续四周上涨后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 23:29:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：欧元因法国大选影响而下跌，股市小幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-slips-after-french-vote-as-busy-week-begins-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对法国大选后财政状况的担忧，欧元下跌，而受台湾指数上涨的推动，亚洲股市小幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-slips-after-french-vote-as-busy-week-begins-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 22:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星工会发起三天罢工，加大对员工薪酬的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/samsung-union-steps-up-pressure-over-pay-with-three-day-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，超过 6,500 名三星电子公司工人举行罢工，要求提高工资，这是这家韩国企业集团半个世纪历史上规模最大的劳工组织行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/samsung-union-steps-up-pressure-over-pay-with-three-day-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日菲签署防务协议 中菲关系紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/japan-philippines-set-to-sign-key-military-pact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与中国持续紧张的关系中，美国的盟友日本与菲律宾周一签署了一项重要协议，将促进军事人员相互访问。在此背景下，这两个美国盟友加强了防务关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/japan-philippines-set-to-sign-key-military-pact</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 13:18:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
